description.en:
No Taxes, No Bullshit. It’s that simple.
100% of the tokens were sent to the liquidity pool, LP tokens were burnt, and contract is renounced. 
BIBI is the most famous bird in China to bring people luck. $BIBI is a meme coin with no intrinsic value or expectation of financial return.
